            <h1 style="color: #fbbf24; font-size: 26px !important; font-weight: 800; text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,1); margin: 0; font-family: sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">
                የውጊያ ቴክኒክ ትምህርት ቤት
            </h1>
            <p style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 13.5px !important; font-weight: bold; text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,1); margin: 5px 0 0 0; font-style: italic;">
                "እናቅዳለን፤ እንጀምራለን፤ እናሰፋለን፤ በፍጥነት እና በጥራት እንፈጽማለን。"
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 🚜 3. በቀኝ ጫፍ የውጊያ ቴክኒክ ትምህርት ቤት ሎጎ -->
        <div style="flex: 0 0 auto; text-align: right;">
            <img src="/images/logo.png" 
                 onerror="this.src='/image/logo.png'; this.onerror=function(){this.src='/images/logo.jpg';};" 
                 style="height: 85px !important; width: auto; object-fit: contain; filter: drop-shadow(0 3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.8));" 
                 alt="Combat Technic School Logo">
        </div>

    </div>
</header>


