                <div class="training-photo-item"><img src="/images/photo3.jpg" alt="Training 3"></div>
                <div class="training-photo-item"><img src="/images/photo4.jpg" alt="Training 4"></div>

                <!-- 📸 2. አዲሶቹ የአዋሽ አርባ ፎቶዎች (aw1 - aw6) -->
